5.  Three-dimensional plots.  Maple can also provide representations f
or graphs of functions of two variables.  The graphs of such functions
 are surfaces in three-dimensional space.  The Maple command is:" }}
{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 5 "     " }
{TEXT 270 0 "" }{TEXT 271 4 "plot" }{TEXT 272 2 "3d" }{TEXT -1 2 "( " 
